### Create note (happy path)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Manual test note",
  "content": "Created from api/notes/create-note.http"
}

### Create note without title (expected 400)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Missing title should fail validation"
}

### Create note with invalid JSON (expected 400)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Broken JSON",
  "content": "Missing closing quote
}
